</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x3_d_image_sharpen_desktop__is_supported" kindref="compound">IsSupported</ref>   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Checks if Sharpen Desktop is supported on a GPU.       </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><ref refid="_d_o_x__i_a_d_l_x3_d_image_sharpen_desktop__set_enabled" kindref="compound">SetEnabled</ref>   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Sets Sharpen Desktop to enabled or disabled on a GPU.      </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
